After this time, the company evaluates the group s progress and determines whether they ll further invest and cultivate based on its standing/ success in the industry. Similarly, members can also consider whether to renew the contract after twoyears as per their initial seven-year contract. If AND ONLY IF the group still has great potential for development and the members renew their contracts, the company will continue to map out development strategies for the coming years and create new lore/storylines. The result of this comeback and also tour might directly affect the boys  futurecareer, determining whether they ll still continue as txt beyond the initial 7 years or not. We all know Hybe never does txt any justice compared to other groups in terms of marketing and promotions but this time they really went all out, which is considered a  desperate move  during such period of time.
